title: Fly into the updated KSFO San Francisco International Airport in MSFS
description:
A significant update for San Francisco International Airport has been released. One important note is that the default San Francisco International Airport must be removed to avoid conflicts with this add-on. Once you see this add-on, you'll likely agree that it's an obvious choice.

For a full overview of items added to the marketplace this week have a look at the video below:
